<!-- wp:maysternya/text-image {"title":"BIOGRAPHY","content":"Leonid Sadovsky is a Ukrainian theater director, teacher, and the founder of MAYSTERNYA 55. Born in Kharkiv in 1965, he graduated from the Kharkiv National University of Arts with a degree in Theater Directing in 1989.\n\nAfter working in various state theaters across Ukraine, Sadovsky founded MAYSTERNYA 55 in 2006 as an independent theater studio dedicated to creating authentic, emotionally powerful performance work. His vision combined the psychological depth of the Stanislavski tradition with physical theater techniques drawn from European masters.\n\nUnder his leadership, MAYSTERNYA 55 has grown from a small studio into one of Ukraine's most respected independent theater companies, with productions touring internationally and educational programs reaching hundreds of young artists.","imagePosition":"right"} /-->

